graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks - Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|base OS & runtime| UBI[UBI8/UBI9 Base Images]
    Notebooks -->|interactive UI| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.2-3.6]
    Notebooks -->|notebook server| NotebookServer[Jupyter Notebook 6.4-6.5]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 1.x/2.x]
    Notebooks -->|GPU acceleration| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit 11.x/12.x]
    Notebooks -->|data analysis| NumPy[NumPy]
    Notebooks -->|data analysis| Pandas[Pandas]
    Notebooks -->|ML library| ScikitLearn[Scikit-learn]
    Notebooks -->|computer vision| OpenCV[OpenCV]
    Notebooks -->|pipeline orchestration| Elyra[Elyra 3.x]
    Notebooks -->|IDE| CodeServerPkg[code-server]
    Notebooks -->|R IDE| RStudioPkg[RStudio Server]
    Notebooks -->|cluster CLI| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI oc]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|launches workbenches| NotebookController[Notebook Controller]
    Notebooks -->|UI selection| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    Notebooks -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
    Notebooks -->|pipeline execution| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines KFP]
    Notebooks -->|model storage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Notebooks -.->|service mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - mTLS]

    %% Integration Points (reverse direction - components that use notebooks)
    Dashboard -->|displays images| Notebooks
    NotebookController -->|creates StatefulSets| Notebooks
    KFP -->|executes runtime images| Notebooks

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage]
    Notebooks -->|image registry| Quay[quay.io/modh/*]
    Notebooks -->|package install| PyPI[PyPI / Conda]
    Notebooks -->|source control| GitHub[GitHub]
    Notebooks -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]

